name: James
text: OK suppose to be preloaded but they won't start loading your trailer till you actually arrive and have to sit and wait on it to be loaded like a live load.. been here since 6am. They don't start till 730 am.. won't even let you in the gate till your load is ready..

name: abby bakalov
text: Our driver was delivering early the previous load and went to the facility for pick up  a day early.He check in at 8:30 am in the morning,and ask can they load him a day early  and they set to  wait ,so at 15:00 they told him to come back tomorrow,cant load him today.The driver come back next day at 6:30 in the morning,they give him door at 12:00and his  trailer are loaded at 13:10.They have only one person to loading and same person for uploading.

name: soylent green
text: I do business here five days a week so I know these people. They are a pleasure to deal with and are always smiling. For me (a guy) its especially nice that all the women are beautiful and charming. One of my favorite stops.

name: TheSexsar
text: Working as a dedicated BASF account this customer is fast unloading and loading have not complaints about it

name: Mike Robson
text: New HOURS 6am-5:30pm for live shipping and receiving. 24/7 Drop and Hook for containers and pre-load tractors. Overnight parking. Check in with the guard.

name: Predrag Rakocevic
text: Slow slow slow , if your broker told you something don't believe them. Receiving starts at 12:30 pm so take a number and wait!
